            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_014gKFk1jDnozyfwrBfe2rjK\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Got it! Now let's talk about your **solution** — how does Friend of the Pod actually solve the pain points for your users?\\n\\nIn other words:\\n- **For hosts:** What's the step-by-step experience? How does the AI matching work? What do they get?\\n- **For guests:** How do they benefit? What's easy about it?\\n\\nThink about the tangible outcomes: faster bookings, better guest quality, more exposure, etc.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Now let's talk about your solution — how does Friend of the Pod actually solve the pain points for your users? For hosts: What's the step-by-step experience? How does the AI matching work? What do they get? For guests: How do they benefit? What's easy about it? Think about the tangible outcomes: faster bookings, better guest quality, more exposure, etc.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2673,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":207,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
