            "size": 1538,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01MJfm3waDGJapnCsdVp4pay\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! Now let's move to **social proof**. \\n\\nThis is about building credibility on your landing page. Social proof can be:\\n- **Testimonials** from early users (hosts or guests who've had success)\\n- **Your founder story** — why you're the right person to build this\\n- **Your background/expertise** — podcast industry experience, AI/tech chops, etc.\\n- **Early traction** — number of matches made, podcasts using the platform, etc.\\n- **Press mentions** or industry recognition\\n\\nWhat social proof do you have, or what's your angle for building trust with visitors?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Now let's move to social proof. This is about building credibility on your landing page. Social proof can be: testimonials from early users (hosts or guests who've had success), your founder story — why you're the right person to build this, your background/expertise — podcast industry experience, AI/tech chops, etc., or early traction — number of matches made, podcasts using the platform, etc. What social proof do you have, or what's your angle for building trust with visitors?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2867,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":267,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
