        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1668,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1668,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01CvVCcwEhPuwEZsvmcjegAa\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I get it—you're having fun! But I need you to actually engage with this brainstorming session so we can build something real.\\n\\nLet me be direct: **Friend of the Pod is your business idea.** I need you to answer this one question clearly:\\n\\n**Who does Friend of the Pod match, and what problem does it solve?**\\n\\nPick one:\\n- Are you helping **podcast listeners** find shows they'll love?\\n- Are you helping **podcast creators** find guests?\\n- Are you helping **podcasters** find collaboration partners?\\n- Something else?\\n\\nOnce you give me a straight answer, we'll move through the rest of the brainstorming quickly and get to building your landing page.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need a real answer here. Friend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service—but who are you matching and what problem are you solving? Give me one clear sentence.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"We help podcast listeners discover shows they'll actually love based on their listening habits\\\",\\n    \\\"We help indie podcasters find the perfect guests for their episodes\\\",\\n    \\\"We connect podcasters with similar audiences for cross-promotion and collaboration\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Pick one direction and let's move forward.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3220,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":292,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
