            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01VK99JydJ3YCPQxPGompTzD\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great! I can see your **Launch10** logo—it's a vibrant, modern design with a rocket, gradient background, and a clear startup/growth vibe. This gives me good context for the look and feel later.\\n\\nNow, let's start with the foundation: **your core business idea.**\\n\\nI need to understand what Launch10 actually does and what makes it different. Here's what I'm looking for:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Tell me about Launch10. What does it do, and what makes it different from competitors? Think about: What problem does it solve? Who uses it? What's your unique angle?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Launch10 is a done-for-you service that helps solopreneurs launch their first digital product in 10 days—we handle everything from ideation to marketing setup, so they don't have to learn it all themselves.\\\",\\n    \\\"Launch10 is a community + course platform for first-time founders who want to build in public and get feedback from other founders—unlike traditional courses, we focus on accountability and peer learning.\\\",\\n    \\\"Launch10 is an AI-powered tool that generates personalized go-to-market strategies for B2B SaaS startups based on their industry and target customer.\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Give me 2-3 sentences about what Launch10 does and what makes it stand out.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2860,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":323,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
