          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1526,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_019hk8MRr13rHH68Au79mS9D\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate your interest, but I need your input to create a landing page that truly represents *your* business idea. I can't brainstorm your core concept for you—that's the foundation of everything!\\n\\nLet me make this easier. Just tell me:\\n\\n**What product or service do you want to sell?**\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I know it feels like a lot, but I really need to understand YOUR business idea to help you. Think of it this way: What would you tell a friend you're selling? It doesn't need to be perfect—just give me the basics.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"I'm creating a meal prep service for busy parents that delivers pre-portioned ingredients with 15-minute recipe cards\\\",\\n    \\\"I'm building a project management tool specifically for freelance designers that integrates with Figma and automates client invoicing\\\",\\n    \\\"I'm starting a dog walking service in Brooklyn that sends real-time GPS updates and photos to pet owners\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What's your business idea? Just describe it in a sentence or two—what are you selling and who is it for?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2553,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":266,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
