          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1018,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01EiCYnZR7cwS8x8jqHbnnzN\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I can see the image you've shared - it looks like a \\\"Launch10\\\" logo with a rocket and space theme. However, I'm still waiting to hear about your **target audience** for Friend of the Pod.\\n\\nLet me ask again: **Who are you primarily serving?**\\n\\nFor example:\\n- Podcast hosts who run interview shows and need a steady stream of quality guests\\n- Thought leaders and authors who want to get booked on podcasts to promote their work  \\n- B2B SaaS founders who struggle to find relevant podcast opportunities in their niche\\n\\n**Who's your main audience, and what specific pain points keep them up at night?**\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3428,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":144,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
