            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01J1mcrXZXFWZLKHwHM9G3em\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I don't see any product photos uploaded yet. You can upload images now using the Brand Personalization panel on the left sidebar - just look for the image upload section. Once you've added your hero images there, hit 'Build My Site' and I'll make sure they're featured prominently in your hero section. Want to upload those images now, or would you like to build with smart defaults first and add images later?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4110,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":113,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
